title: Inspector Rex S2 Ep28 - Go-Cart
description:
Inspector Rex S2 Ep28 - Go-Cart

Go-Cart - Martin, an employee at a go-cart track, desperately wants to become a race-driver. But he needs money and he has already borrowed from a loan shark and is falling behind in his payments. When the loan shark is killed, Inspector Brandtner and Rex are called in to investigate. Stars Gedeon Burkhard, Heinz Weixelbraun and Martin Weinek.

From Austria, in German, English subtitles

Subtitles by SBS AU TV
